# Line-ending policy.
# Scripts launched through the scriptPath-Workflow permission validator
# (orchestrator/processes/*.mjs) MUST be LF — a CR byte (U+000D) makes the
# Windows validator reject the whole file, blocking the launch (FB-LR-27,
# DEC-DEV-0114). Pin the script families to LF so the source never ships CRLF.
*.mjs text eol=lf
*.cjs text eol=lf
*.js  text eol=lf
*.sh  text eol=lf
